                <h2 class="cs_post_title cs_lh_base cs_fs_26 cs_fs_lg_18 cs_mb_20"><a href="{{ url('global-industry-leaders-eager-to-share-insights-at-ngsc') }}">Global Industry Leaders Eager to Share Insights at the New Global Sport Conference in Riyadh</a></h2>
                <p>• “The New Global Sport Conference in Riyadh provides a convergence of innovation, passion, collaboration, and excellence” - Joe Marsh, CEO, T1 Entertainment & Sports.</p>
